answers.body_markdown:
Found the answer. I should have looked in the it0025 example. What needs to be added to the `pom.xml` of the dependent project is
```
      &lt;plugin&gt;
        &lt;groupId&gt;com.github.maven-nar&lt;/groupId&gt;
        &lt;artifactId&gt;nar-maven-plugin&lt;/artifactId&gt;
        &lt;version&gt;${nar-plugin.version}&lt;/version&gt;
        &lt;extensions&gt;true&lt;/extensions&gt;
        &lt;executions&gt;
          &lt;execution&gt;
            &lt;id&gt;nar-download&lt;/id&gt;
            &lt;goals&gt;
              &lt;goal&gt;nar-download&lt;/goal&gt;
            &lt;/goals&gt;
          &lt;/execution&gt;
          &lt;execution&gt;
            &lt;id&gt;nar-test-unpack&lt;/id&gt;
            &lt;goals&gt;
              &lt;goal&gt;nar-test-unpack&lt;/goal&gt;
            &lt;/goals&gt;
          &lt;/execution&gt;
          &lt;execution&gt;
            &lt;id&gt;nar-integration-test&lt;/id&gt;
            &lt;goals&gt;
              &lt;goal&gt;nar-integration-test&lt;/goal&gt;
            &lt;/goals&gt;
          &lt;/execution&gt;
        &lt;/executions&gt;
      &lt;/plugin&gt;
```

